{"tid":1867261,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同個肥婆同事講想要個口罩..點知佢俾左佢個Bra我","createTime":"2020-02-07T06:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T09:45:06.000Z","uid":8968,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4681f9f05314bbb0d8e057a7b117f26f088feb","tid":1867261,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"是甘的<br />\n今日食完Lunch先發覺唔記得左帶多個口罩換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁岩見到公司個死肥婆枱面有一盒口罩, <br />\n米死死地氣問佢 「喂!俾個罩我得唔得?」<br />\n點知佢面紅紅咁話你等我一陣 因間拎俾你, 就衝左出去<br />\n<br />\n發覺佢都神神地之後返埋位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過左大約5分鐘佢行埋黎, 對手擺後面好似收埋D乜咁<br />\n屌, 佢一遞出黎係佢個Bra...佢就咁擺低左係我枱面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲未驚訝完, 佢就用盡全身脂肪既力閃走左<br />\n<br />\n各位手足, 我點處置呢個罩好(好似好撚臭)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2308e4ee15ad2b0c766f40dedef39b0732b60d72","tid":1867261,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d0d3c94520b65d746871c2427cd5b5285878a9","tid":1867261,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f831cf394563f54f2b4c6b4504a56866b987eb","tid":1867261,"uid":60321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"唔要比我<br />\n我無罩用"},{"pid":"c13aba45fc02eae8069e0d72981f2fc91efba751","tid":1867261,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"零分重做"},{"pid":"3f6d4e1ca5c14c6ff377e5d49952a8f35b1e7498","tid":1867261,"uid":95499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"肥婆個bra當面罩用都得 你賺咗啦"},{"pid":"bdb3dabdc72966a20ee2dbb9800fbe3f39fb6d4a","tid":1867261,"uid":8968,"l